 a simple search as in the main page and retrieve all matched metadata.
 The search is usefull because it allows you to focus only on metadata of
 interest.
 Once you add a node of this type, you will get a page like the one shown
 in figure 
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{fig:harvesting-gn}

\end_inset

.
