\begin_layout Section
A note on ownership
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Please, consider that the MEF format version 1.0 does not take into account
 user and group ownership.
 When exporting metadata, you loose this information.
 When importing metadata, the new owner becomes the user that is performing
 the import while the group ownership is set to null.
